---
title: Quick Turkey Irish-Style Stew with Garlic Crostini
description: In this hearty twist on classic potato-and-beef stew, we've swapped in quick-cooking ground turkey so your meal will be on the table in less than 40 minutes. Don't forget to wipe the bowl clean with a slice of garlic crostini!
